# Highlands Map (biome: highlands)
# Symbols (assets/tiles.yaml): . = grass  H = heather  S = stream
#   % = cliff  # = granite  B = ruined wall  = = slate wall
#   T = pine   A = rock outcrop  R = boulder  + = start
#   @ next to start = invisible portal_gate_forest NPC ("return to the forest?")
#   @ near the slate tomb = lich_nexus_entrance
# Monster spawns (match assets/monsters.yaml): c=puma h=elf_archer
#   j=elf_swordsman v=mountain_troll z=archmage q=lich
# Zones: start meadow (S) -> heather moor & pumas (W), pine grove & archers (N),
#   boulder field & trolls (E), central ruins (swordsmen+archmages),
#   far slate tomb (lich, deepest). All areas reachable; ruins/tomb have entrances.
